<TEXT>
<P>
As I happened upon what I thought was a science fiction movie, it instead 
turned out to be "Hard Time on Planet Earth." After watching just 30 minutes of 
it, I can see why it is having such a hard time! 
</P>
<P>
Gary Traxler, North Hollywood 
</P>
