<HEADLINE>
<P>
DEMOCRACY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Concerning the recent historical events in China, Poland and the Soviet Union, 
it has become exquisitely evident that Marx and Lenin were wrong. Religion is 
not the opium of the masses. Democracy and freedom are the opium of the masses! 
Once exposed, the masses become addicted. 
</P>
<P>
DEMETRIOS N. KYRIACOU 
</P>
<P>
Burbank 
</P>
</TEXT>
