<P>
PROTEST ON PIGGING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I was aghast that Bill Marriott described families as "pigging out" (The Savvy 
Traveler, June 11) in his hotels. First, the condescension toward families is 
evident in his terminology, and secondly, Marriott hotels should not have 
offered the bargain to families if it did not want their business. 
</P>
<P>
SALLY MONROE 
