<P>
My wife and I look forward eagerly to your Travel Section every Sunday and 
enjoy reading about all the places that we hope to visit some day. We 
especially enjoyed the June 18 article by Georgia Hesse -- "Voyaging Between 
the 'Lost Islands' of Micronesia." But the article's dateline puzzled us since 
