<HEADLINE>
<P>
LOST EL CAJON MAN SAFE AFTER 5 DAYS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A 32-year-old mentally impaired El Cajon man missing for five days was found 
Saturday after being noticed by some Del Mar residents, sheriff's deputies 
said. 
</P>
<P>
David Allan Powers, who disappeared from the Del Mar Fair after he wandered 
away from his mother Tuesday, was found at a Del Mar gas station, deputies 
said. 
</P>
<P>
Powers was in good condition and released to his guardian, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
Deputies were dispatched to 12th Street and Camino Del Mar after they received 
several calls from residents who said they had seen the El Cajon man. 
</P>
</TEXT>
