CALIFORNIA -- BUDGET; CALIFORNIA -- FINANCES; CALIFORNIA -- POLITICS; SPECIAL 
INTEREST GROUPS; GOVERNMENT SPENDING; CALIFORNIA -- TRANSPORTATION; WELFARE 
PROGRAMS -- CALIFORNIA; CALIFORNIA -- SCHOOLS -- FINANCES; PROPOSITION 98 
(SCHOOL DISTRICT FUNDS); CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
